#steam
######

Open Armory, a community random weapon mod

[h1]Collection of additions to randomized weapon generation.[/h1]

Would you like your weapon designs featured in this mod? Please share your work with us on the [URL=http://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/discussion/802382977/208684375425094063/]steam suggestions thread[/URL], or in the [url=community.playstarbound.com/threads/126973/]forum thread![/url]

Currently features a lot of stuff.
-tealsummernights: axe, hammer and spear blades, broadsword, shortsword, dagger, staff, wand, grenade launcher, machine pistol, assault rifle, shotgun, sniper rifle and rocket launcher pieces
-ihcathb: axe, spear, hammer, broadsword, shortsword, dagger, pistol, machine pistol, shotgun, grenade launcher, assault rifle, sniper rifle and rocket launcher pieces

Integrated with [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=836238594]Grand Armory[/url], [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=780877247]Quarterstaff Armory[/url], [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=780443241]Snub-Nose Armory[/url], [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=760396113]Manufacturer's Touch[/url], and [url=community.playstarbound.com/resources/4285/]Expanded Weapon Generation![/url]

[url=community.playstarbound.com/threads/124193/]IHARTS MEGATHREAD[/url]
